<subSubSection id="38E1657AFF833D139787DDABFD07F9CC" pageId="12" pageNumber="11" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="704436F1FF833D139787DDABFA64F9AC" blockId="12.[192,1440,1475,1563]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis id="428FEAE3FF833D139787DDABFEBAFA6C" bold="true" box="[192,349,1475,1499]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">Discussion.</emphasis>
This strictly New World predaceous genus is primarily Neotropical with only one species, 
<taxonomicName id="B7FB4D72FF833D139787DD8BFDB6FA4C" authority="(Dow and Turner)" baseAuthorityName="Dow and Turner" box="[192,593,1507,1531]" class="Insecta" family="Ceratopogonidae" genus="Amerohelea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="frontispina">
<emphasis id="428FEAE3FF833D139787DD8BFF34FA4D" box="[192,211,1507,1530]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="428FEAE3FF833D1397A6DD8BFE8FFA4C" box="[225,360,1507,1531]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">frontispina</emphasis>
(Dow and Turner)
</taxonomicName>
, occurring in the Nearctic region as far north as California and Texas (
<bibRefCitation id="146A4B00FF833D13978FDE6BFDEDF9AC" author="Borkent, A. &amp; W. L. Grogan, Jr." box="[200,522,1539,1563]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11" pagination="1 - 48" refId="ref11587" refString="Borkent, A., and W. L. Grogan, Jr. 2009. Catalog of the New World biting midges north of Mexico (Diptera: Ceratopogonidae). Zootaxa 2273: 1 - 48." type="journal article" year="2009">Borkent and Grogan 2009</bibRefCitation>
). We provide the first Caribbean records of 
<taxonomicName id="B7FB4D72FF833D139354DE6BFB45F9AC" box="[1043,1186,1539,1563]" class="Insecta" family="Ceratopogonidae" genus="Amerohelea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="428FEAE3FF833D139354DE6BFB45F9AC" box="[1043,1186,1539,1563]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">Amerohelea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="08EC7661FF833D1393AEDE6BFA98F9AC" box="[1257,1407,1539,1563]" name="Guadeloupe" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">Guadeloupe</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
